                      <td valign="top" class="subhead2"><b>23 Aug 2005</b></td>
                      <td align="left" valign="top"><p>HKIX has revised its route server policy on filtering of BGP route announced by the HKIX members. For HKIX members who are using AS filtering and advertising more than 2500 prefixes for 200+ different ASes to the HKIX are entitled to apply for the Closer Peering Arrangement (CPA) with the route server. Please read <a href="route-policy.htm">here</a> for details.</p>
